iterarischen Traditionen des Männerromans nachgeht. Es entsteht das reichhaltige Bild eines Genres, das sich (nicht nur) zwischen Ratgeber und Comedy bewegt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aGerman literaturey21st centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aGerman literaturey21st centuryxThemes, motives. 0aMasculinity in literature. 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aGegenwartsliteratur. 4aGender Studies. 4aGender. 4aGenre. 4aGermanistik. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMännlichkeit. 4aPopkultur. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aContemporary Literature.  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aGenre.  aGerman Literature.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMasculinity.  aPopular Culture.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2015z9783110438673oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070099208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839433096zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839433096423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839433096/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-070099-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DKUb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016